text: Precinct is an unincorporated community in Bollinger County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Precinct was established in 1902, and closed in 1904. The community most likely was named for an election precinct located in or around the original town site. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Bollinger County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Precinct, Missouri
